OL,3,CReservoirs less than half full across
OL,4,C12 sites in England including in
OL,5,CCumbria
OL,7,FReservoir levels dropped below 50% in
OL,8,F12 locations in England by the end of
OL,9,Flast month, with a handful of sites
OL,10,Fonly a third full, figures show.
OL,12,FAffected areas include reservoirs in
OL,13,FCumbria, Somerset and Staffordshire,
OL,14,Fas well as groups of reservoirs in
OL,15,FDerbyshire and across the Yorkshire
OL,16,Fregion.
