OL,7,FTotal reservoir storage for England
OL,8,Fwas 57% of the long-term average at
OL,9,Fthe end of August, down from 69% at
OL,10,Fthe end of July, according to the
OL,11,FEnvironment Agency.
OL,13,FThis was despite heavy rain during the
OL,14,Ffinal days of the month.
OL,16,FSeveral areas of England remain
OL,17,Fcovered by hosepipe bans and are
OL,18,Fofficially in drought after the
OL,19,Fwarmest spring and summer on record.
